'''[[巴西|巴西]][[互聯網|互聯網]]'''於1988年啟用，2011年，巴西有8900萬人為[[網民|網民]]，佔全體人口45％，在全球排名第五​​<ref name=ITU-IndividualsUsingTheInternet>[http://www.itu.int/ITU-D/ict/statistics/material/excel/Individuals%20using%20the%20Internet2000-2011.xls Percentage of Individuals using the Internet 2000-2011] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itu.int/ITU-D/ict/statistics/material/excel/Individuals%20using%20the%20Internet2000-2011.xls |date=20180928224151 }}, International Telecommunication Union</ref>。

== 使用情況 ==
[[.br|.br]]為巴西[[國家及地區頂級域|國家及地區頂級域]]的[[域名|域名]]，由[[巴西互聯網指導委員會|巴西互聯網指導委員會]]管理<ref>[http://www.cgi.br/english/activities/index.htm "Services"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722092844/http://www.cgi.br/english/activities/index.htm |date=2012-07-22 }}, Brazilian Internet Steering Committee (CGI.br)</ref>。在2012年4月，巴西國內使用了48572160個[[IPv4|IPv4]]位址（每1000人約擁有236個），在全球排名第10位<ref>[http://www.countryipblocks.net/country-blocks/select-formats/ Select Formats] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120409181609/http://www.countryipblocks.net/country-blocks/select-formats/ |date=2012-04-09 }}, Country IP Blocks. </ref>。

2010年，巴西國內有13266310個固定寬頻用戶（每1000人中有約68人），在全球排名第9<ref name="2010itu">[http://www.itu.int/ITU-D/ict/statistics/material/excel/2010/FixedBroadbandInternetSubscriptions_00-10.xls Fixed broadband subscriptions] {{Wayback|url=http://www.itu.int/ITU-D/ict/statistics/material/excel/2010/FixedBroadbandInternetSubscriptions_00-10.xls |date=20120925124130 }}, International Telecommunication Union.</ref>。2011年，巴西國內有23,456,00台互聯網主機，在全球排名第四<ref>[https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2184rank.html "Internet hosts"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/rankorder/2184rank.html |date=20170713172440 }}, ''CIA World Factbook'', U.S. Central Intelligence Agency</ref>。

在巴西，互聯網是官民流行的溝通媒介，亦是政府收稅的方式之一，例如99％的[[所得稅|所得稅]]是在網上徵收<ref>[http://g1.globo.com/Sites/Especiais/Noticias/0,,MUL1070812-16725,00-VEJA+AS+DESVANTAGENS+DE+FAZER+A+DECLARACAO+DO+IR+EM+PAPEL.html "Veja as desvantagens de fazer a declaração do IR em papel"] {{Wayback|url=http://g1.globo.com/Sites/Especiais/Noticias/0,,MUL1070812-16725,00-VEJA+AS+DESVANTAGENS+DE+FAZER+A+DECLARACAO+DO+IR+EM+PAPEL.html |date=20200729134254 }}, Ligia Guimarães, Globo.com, 3 April 2009.</ref>。巴西網上很流行[[門戶網站|門戶網站]]、[[社交網絡|社交網絡]]、[[搜索引擎|搜索引擎]]<ref name=eg>[http://www.alexa.com/topsites/countries/BR "Top Sites in Brazil"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.alexa.com/topsites/countries/BR |date=20210317221243 }}, Alexa</ref> 、[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]<ref>[http://diariodonordeste.globo.com/materia.asp?codigo=666764 "Messenger completa dez anos de existência" (Messenger completes ten years of existence)] {{Wayback|url=http://diariodonordeste.globo.com/materia.asp?codigo=666764 |date=20130709003418 }}, Gustavo Pellizzon, Diário do Nordeste (Verdes Mares Ltda.), 31 August 2009</ref>等等的網上服務，例如[[Globo.com|Globo.com]]、[[谷歌|谷歌]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]、[[MSN_Messenger|MSN Messenger]]等<ref name=eg />。

== 光纖到戶服務 ==
[[西班牙電信|西班牙電信]]在[[聖保羅|聖保羅]]推出了[[光纖到戶|光纖到戶]]服務，速度介符30-100Mbit/s；據報導，西班牙電信有400000個住戶用戶，20,000個簽約用戶。到2011年底，西班牙電信計劃在2015年將覆蓋率提高到大約100萬個家庭<ref>[http://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2011/06/27/telefonica-expands-brazilian-ftth-coverage/ "Telefonica expands Brazilian FTTH coverage"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2011/06/27/telefonica-expands-brazilian-ftth-coverage/ |date=20161220214544 }}, TeleGeography, 27 Jun 2011</ref>。{{link-en|巴西電信|Brasil Telecom}}亦提供同類服務，速度達100 Mbit/s，在巴西的10個州提供服務<ref>[http://www.elevatemarketaccesstool.com/emat/telecoms/brazils-oi-makes-a-net-profit-in-q4/ "Brazil’s Oi makes a net profit in Q4"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703195012/http://www.elevatemarketaccesstool.com/emat/telecoms/brazils-oi-makes-a-net-profit-in-q4/ |date=2013-07-03 }}, EMAT-ELEVATE in Latin America, 8 March 2011</ref>。{{link-en|地球村電信|Global Village Telecom}}在56個城市提供光纖到戶服務，包括[[阿雷格里港|阿雷格里港]]、[[庫里蒂巴|庫里蒂巴]]、[[貝洛奧里藏特|貝洛奧里藏特]]等，速度達100 Mbit/s<ref>[http://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2010/10/12/global-village-telecom-boasts-one-million-broadband-users/ "Global Village Telecom boasts one million broadband users"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegeography.com/products/commsupdate/articles/2010/10/12/global-village-telecom-boasts-one-million-broadband-users/ |date=20161220214616 }}, TeleGeography, 12 October 2010</ref>。

